I apologize in advance. XD






Clay sighed as the sun streaming through the cheap blinds.  As he moved, the dusky-skinned woman next to him did as well.  For a second, the big cowboy's sleep fogged brain reached for a name; the one he was always on the look out for.  But no; the sleeping woman next to him turned and while her features were obviously Indian; it was the wrong sort of Indian. 

'Really from India' Indian.

Lalita.   Oooooooooooooh boy, had that been the most awkward sex he'd ever had.

When the shapely Asian babe had approached him for something physical, at first Clay had been pissed.  After all, Lali was his friend, Evan's, girlfriend.  It would simply not be right to run around on a friend.

Then, Evan had pulled him aside and explained that though he and Lali shared an emotional bond, Evan was physically incapable of intercourse.  Nailing Lalita would be nothing more than a favor between them.

Clay should have run very, very far away, but, aimiable to a fault, he'd agreed to add a little buckaroo to the mix.

This was *so* going to come back to bite him on the ass.

There was a snort from behind him and a well-muscled, much scarred arm slipped around Clay's waist.

And there was the OTHER reason that was the most awkward night he'd ever spent.

During a lull in the action, Evan had slipped in the door and pronounced his jealousy.

And for some silly reason, Clay had assumed Evan had been jealous of *him* for screwing Lalita.

Why the hell had he agreed to any of this?  He couldn't quite recall.  Was he drunk?  Nnooooo, he hadn't had anything to drink yesterday; no help there.

Evan shifted closer to him in sleep as Lalita  rolled over again.

Clay gritted his teeth.  Why hadn't he seen this coming?  Evan never said flat out he was bisexual, but he had admitted to finding some men attractive.  That was pretty much the same thing, right? There had even been a few times when Evan had mentioned Clay being very attractive, but the big cowboy had brushed it off as one of those 'Oh, you look good today' comments.

It was true Evan was just as incapable of intercourse with a man as he was with a woman, and Clay hadn't had the urge to do any pitching to anyone but Lali, so no actual penetration had occurred; technically, they hadn't had sex.

But if anyone should ask if he'd ever 'been' with a man before, Clay couldn't say no.

Lalita snuggled up to Clay's chest.  The big cowboy slipped an arm around her waist more out of instinct than any warm fuzzy feelings.  Evan shifted to hug both of his bed partners.  In the same breath, Evan and Lalita let out a long-deep sigh of contentment.

Clay squeaked.
